<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>إِذَا حَكَى لِي طَمَعٌ رَاحَةً ...<span style="color:#006d98"> قُلْتُ لَهُ:</span> الرَّاحَةُ فِي الْيَأْسِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
